exceptions.tactic: apply diagram_comp with (X:=X) (Y:=Y) (Z:=Y) (X':=X) (Y':=Y) (RX:=TX) (RY:=R) (R:=TY) (RY':=TY')(S:=comp (star S) R) (S':=comp (star S) R').
exceptions.exn: In environment X : Set S, TX : relation X HS : diagram TX S (star TX) (plus S) Hwf : well_founded (trans S) Hpwf := plus_wf Hwf : well_founded (trans (plus S)) TX' : relation X HS' : diagram TX' S (comp (star TX) TX') (plus S) Y : Type R, R' : relation2 X Y TY, TY' : relation Y HR : diagram TX R (star TY) (comp (star S) R) HR' : diagram TX' R (comp (star TY) TY') (comp (star S) R') The term "R" has type "X -> Y -> Prop" while it is expected to have type "Y -> Y -> Prop" (cannot unify "Y" and "X").

In environment r : forall X Y Z : Type, relation2 X Y -> relation2 Y Z -> relation2 X Z H : forall (X Y Z X' Y' Z' : Type) (RY : relation2 Y Y') (RX : relation2 X X') (R1 : relation2 X Y) (R2 : relation2 Y Z) (RZ : relation2 Z Z') (S1 : relation2 X' Y') (S2 : relation2 Y' Z'), diagram RX R1 RY S1 -> diagram RY R2 RZ S2 -> diagram RX (comp R1 R2) RZ (comp S1 S2) X : Set S, TX : relation X HS : diagram TX S (star TX) (plus S) Hwf : well_founded (trans S) TX' : relation X HS' : diagram TX' S (comp (star TX) TX') (plus S) Y : Type R, R' : relation2 X Y TY, TY' : relation Y HR : diagram TX R (star TY) (comp (star S) R) HR' : diagram TX' R (comp (star TY) TY') (comp (star S) R') Unable to unify "diagram TX R (star TY) (comp (star S) R)" with "diagram (r X X X (star TX) TX') (r X X Y (star S) R) (r Y Y Y (star TY) TY') (r X X Y (star S) R')".

In environment X0 : forall X Y Z : Type, relation2 X Y -> relation2 Y Z -> relation2 X Z H0 : forall (X Y Z X' Y' Z' : Type) (RY : relation2 Y Y') (RX : relation2 X X') (R1 : relation2 X Y) (R2 : relation2 Y Z) (RZ : relation2 Z Z') (S1 : relation2 X' Y') (S2 : relation2 Y' Z'), diagram RX R1 RY S1 -> diagram RY R2 RZ S2 -> diagram RX (comp R1 R2) RZ (comp S1 S2) r : forall X Y Z : Type, relation2 X Y -> relation2 Y Z -> relation2 X Z X : Set S, TX : relation X HS : diagram TX S (star TX) (plus S) Hwf : well_founded (trans S) TX' : relation X HS' : diagram TX' S (comp (star TX) TX') (plus S) Y : Type R, R' : relation2 X Y TY, TY' : relation Y HR : diagram TX R (star TY) (comp (star S) R) HR' : diagram TX' R (comp (star TY) TY') (comp (star S) R') Unable to unify "diagram TX' R (comp (star TY) TY') (comp (star S) R')" with "diagram (r X X X (star TX) TX') (r X X Y (star S) R) (r Y Y Y (star TY) TY') (r X X Y (star S) R')".
